Welcome to the Cookulator Mobile App

Last changed: Tuesday, April 29, 2014 5:35pm EST

----------------------------------

Scenario: 
 - Jenny has just moved to the United States from Japan and found a new recipe 
   for Teriyaki Chicken at the local grocery store. However, she is unfamiliar 
   with the units of measurement that were on the recipe. She wishes she could 
   convert these amounts into mL (milliliter) measurements so she can use her 
   old measuring cup that she has already unpacked.

----------------------------------

Features:
 - Basic Calculator
 - Unit Conversions (Distance, Weight, Volume) automatically run through change events
 - Ability to store calculations and conversions in the Notes page
 - Shake to clear functionality

